homeQuickWord: A quick word from our sponsors:
strapline: React components for faster and easier web development. Build your own design system, or start with Material Design.
installDescr: Install Material-UI's source files via npm. We take care of injecting the CSS needed.
usageDescr: Material-UI components work without any additional setup, and don't pollute the global scope.
themesDescr: Take Material-UI to the next level with premium themes from our official marketplace – all built on Material-UI.
adblock: If you don't mind tech-related ads, and want to support Open Source, please whitelist Material-UI in your ad blocker.
adTitle: This ad is designed to support Open Source.
mdbProDescr: Material Dashboard Pro React is a premium Material-UI admin theme.
mkProDescr: An awesome Material-UI Kit based on Material Design.
mdbDescr: Material Dashboard React is a free Material-UI admin theme.
mkDescr: A free Material-UI Kit based on Material Design.
pbDescr: A page that mimics Firebase. This item includes theming using the ThemeProvider component.
opDescr: An example landing and Sign Up page.
instaDescr: A recreation of Instagram's profile page by customizing Material-UI's theme.
tweeperDescr: A recreation of Twitter's profile page by customizing Material-UI's theme.
dashboardDescr: A minimal dashboard with taskbar and mini variant draw. The chart is courtesy of Recharts, but it is simple to substitute an alternative.
signInSideDescr: A simple Sign In side page.
blogDescr: A sophisticated blog page layout. Markdown support is courtesy of markdown-to-jsx but is easily replaced.

albumDescr: A responsive album / gallery page layout with a hero unit and footer.
